OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782411505
OL,3,CFoo Fighters fans urged to stay safe
OL,4,Cas heatwave hits stadium gigs
OL,6,FFoo Fighters are set to take the stage
OL,7,Fat Anfield for two massive shows, but
OL,8,Fconcertgoers are being issued urgent
OL,9,Fsafety advice as high temperatures
OL,10,Fsweep across the UK.
OL,12,FThe American rock legends will perform
OL,13,Fat the home of Liverpool FC on
OL,14,FThursday, June 25, and again on
OL,15,FSaturday, 27 June.
OL,17,FTemperatures have soared well above 30
OL,18,Fdegrees over the last week and an
OL,19,Famber weather warning is in place
OL,20,Facross the North West until Thursday
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
