OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782411505
OL,3,CFoo Fighters fans urged to stay safe
OL,4,Cas heatwave hits stadium gigs
OL,6,FOrganisers are warning fans to prepare
OL,7,Ffor the weather well before the gig
OL,8,Fstarts. From hydration stations to
OL,9,Fsecurity checks, here's everything you
OL,10,Fneed to know if you're heading to the
OL,11,Fconcert:
OL,13,FBefore you head to Anfield
OL,15,FOnce inside the stadium
OL,17,FAnfield has adapted its usual security
OL,18,Fpolicies to help fans cope with the
OL,19,Fsummer heat, but some strict
OL,20,Frestrictions remain in place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782411505
OL,3,CFoo Fighters fans urged to stay safe
OL,4,Cas heatwave hits stadium gigs
OL,6,FWhat you can bring: You are allowed to
OL,7,Fbring one sealed 500ml clear, soft
OL,8,Fplastic bottle of water into the
OL,9,Fground.
OL,11,FReusable soft plastic bottles are also
OL,12,Fallowed, but they must be completely
OL,13,Ftransparent. Metal and glass bottles
OL,14,Fare strictly prohibited.
OL,16,FOnce inside, there are several ways to
OL,17,Fkeep your bottle topped up:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782411505
OL,3,CFoo Fighters fans urged to stay safe
OL,4,Cas heatwave hits stadium gigs
OL,6,FIf you forget your sun cream, don't
OL,7,Fpanic. Sunscreen dispensers will be
OL,8,Favailable upon entry, inside the
OL,9,Fstadium, and at all medical and
OL,10,Fwelfare facilities.
OL,12,FKnowing the signs of heat exhaustion
OL,14,FWhile everyone wants to enjoy a
OL,15,Fmemorable night, emergency services
OL,16,Fand stewards are asking fans to look
OL,17,Fout for one another.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
