PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782411505
OL,3,CFoo Fighters fans urged to stay safe
OL,4,Cas heatwave hits stadium gigs
OL,6,FConcertgoers should take immediate
OL,7,Fnote of any signs of heat exhaustion,
OL,8,Fwhich include dizziness, nausea,
OL,9,Fgoosebumps, or suddenly feeling cold
OL,10,Fdespite the hot weather.
OL,12,FIf you or anyone around you feels
OL,13,Funwell, find your nearest stadium
OL,14,Fsteward or head to a medical facility
OL,15,Fimmediately.
OL,17,FOrganisers said: "We want all fans to
OL,18,Fenjoy a safe and memorable experience.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
