CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782411505
OL,3,CFoo Fighters fans urged to stay safe
OL,4,Cas heatwave hits stadium gigs
OL,6,FBy following this guidance and looking
OL,7,Fout for each other, we can ensure the
OL,8,Fshows will be another two special
OL,9,Fnights at Anfield."
